title: Merrimen Strong Heavy Duty Clear Packaging Tape - 12 Rolls (48MM x 66M) - Secure Sticky Sealing Tape for Parcel Boxes, Moving Boxes & Large Postal Bags - Ideal for Long Term Storage
features: EXTRA THICK & DURABLE: Our heavy-duty Fragile tape boasts an impressive 45-micron thickness, ensuring resilience against wear and tear for prolonged use. Its exceptional adhesion provides a robust hold and seal.
NO CRACKING & PEELING: Engineered to resist UV rays and moisture, our heavy duty tape remains crack and peel-resistant even in temperatures ranging from -23°C to 93°C.

STICKY & RELIABLE: Crafted with high-quality materials, our adhesive tape adheres exceptionally well to cardboard paper and similar surfaces. For added protection in delicate or heavy shipments, layering is easy, providing extra peace of mind.

NO DISCOLOURATION: Our clear tapes are acrylic-based and resistant to aging, weathering, and yellowing, our parcel tape is ideal for long-term storage. Rest assured that this tape maintains its stickiness and strength over extended periods.

MULTI-USE: More than just a packing tape and packaging tape, it's perfect for wrapping, moving, labeling, and shipping. Choose from convenient 3-pack, 6-pack, 12-pack, and 24-pack variants to meet your specific needs.
